caller_intent: The caller is attempting to take over a mobile home insurance policy that was canceled by another party (Audrey) and seeks clarification on coverage details, including storage insurance.
resolution_steps: Agent confirms the mobile home's address (1646 Chardell Drive, Unit 39) and acknowledges the cancellation.
Agent commits to generating a quote and sending it via email by the end of the week.
Agent explains storage coverage terms (10% of personal property amount applies to stored items).
Agent schedules a follow-up discussion to review the quote and finalize the policy.
summary: A caller seeks to assume a canceled mobile home insurance policy and clarify storage coverage terms. The agent confirms details, commits to providing a quote by Friday, and explains storage coverage as 10% of personal property value. The conversation concludes with a plan to email the quote and schedule a follow-up.
